PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt1Intro::
    .string "This tower is rich\n"
    .string "with lingering SOULS.\p"
    .string "These spirits hold\n"
    .string "enormous energy.$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt1Defeat::
    .string "I give up!$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt1PostBattle::
    .string "I'm not going to forget this!$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt2Intro::
    .string "That old man knows\n"
    .string "too much about SOULS.\p"
    .string "Boss wants him alive.$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt2Defeat::
    .string "Please!\n"
    .string "No more!$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt2PostBattle::
    .string "POKéMON are only good for making\n"
    .string "money. Why not use them?\p"
    .string "You stay out of our business!$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt3Intro::
    .string "You're not saving anyone, kid!$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt3Defeat::
    .string "Don't fight us ROCKETS!$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_Grunt3PostBattle::
    .string "Just SOULS\n"
    .string "that refused to fade.$"

PokemonTower_7F_Text_MrFujiThankYouFollowMe::
    .string "MR. FUJI: You saw it,\n"
    .string "didn't you?\p"
    .string "The Soul of that MAROWAK.\p"
    .string "Souls do not always\n"
    .string "come from battle.\p"
    .string "Sometimes…\p"
    .string "they remain because\n"
    .string "of something stronger.\p"
    .string "Love.\p"
    .string "That MAROWAK stayed\n"
    .string "to protect its CUBONE.\p"
    .string "Even after death.\p"
    .string "That is the true nature\n"
    .string "of Souls.\p"
    .string "Strength that refuses\n"
    .string "to disappear.\p"
    .string "Trainers borrow\n"
    .string "that strength in battle.\p"
    .string "But it was never\n"
    .string "meant to be taken\n"
    .string "by force.\p"
    .string "Follow me to my home, POKéMON\n"
    .string "HOUSE, at the foot of this tower.$"

